{"tid":1980191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢實驗室否認是病毒來源　稱很早已公開全基因組序列","createTime":"2020-04-20T02:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T05:36:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec1ed459ad2fe543b54c4fb41cf6e8f6964748d","tid":1980191,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"武漢國家生物安全實驗室主任袁志明強調，新冠病毒不可能從實驗室外傳。<br />\n<br />\n他接受中國環球電視網訪問時強調，實驗室沒有人受感染，封城期間也沒有人撤走，現時整個研究所都為武漢肺炎病毒進行研究，研發藥物，病毒所亦有嚴格管理，認為外界有這種聯想並不可怕，可怕是有人故意將事情引到實驗室，並指稱美國一名參議員、《華盛頓郵報》及兩名記者寫了文章指病毒來自武漢實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n袁志明認為，人工合成武漢肺炎病毒超越人類智慧，中國很早已經向世衛公開新冠病毒的全基因組序列，為各國提供基礎，開展早期的檢測。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1521471_1_L_20200419153134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1521471_1_L_20200419153134.jpg&h=1b9926fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521471-20200419.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521471-20200419.htm&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=1e209c5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521471-20200419.htm&h=1351ff5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521471-20200419.htm</a>"},{"pid":"171d99d8b0e792d75a15c04132af393c32145b06","tid":1980191,"uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"係不入流的專家，自己蠢！護旗手講大話🤥"},{"pid":"de6c2c8b505bdbbc6461737a5c75be464c2ef24a","tid":1980191,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"扮乜9"},{"pid":"556462b4cbd07c88b2895b37550d453a8845b2de","tid":1980191,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de6c2c8b505bdbbc6461737a5c75be464c2ef24a","tid":1980191,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl